snippet.title: HellRazor64 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The best FPS that never existed finally comes to the modern era! A convict on death row, sentenced to die by electrocution. You awaken in Hell at the mercy of an ancient weapon, the Hellrazor, and you must fulfill its conquest. Reign in Hell or die trying.

Find HellRazor64 on Steam! Available November 17, 2022!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2196140/HellRazor64/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Jeastlickgames?t=m3sKdwq3OFLBbXI6SD_MiQ&s=09
